message_content: Initial contact established. Ready to proceed with the arrangement we discussed.
Good. I've prepared the first installment. When can we move forward?
The overseas connection confirms everything is on schedule. Proceed as planned.
Understood. Will coordinate with local team for the handoff.
Logistics update: All transportation arrangements confirmed for this week.
Jane confirms transport ready. Are your people in position?
Change of plans. The delivery location has been moved to building 7 in the warehouse district.
Building 7 confirmed. Same time as originally planned?
Yes, 11 PM sharp. Make sure you're not followed.
Security protocols have been updated. Use the new authentication phrase: 'Evening Rain'
Authentication phrase received: 'Evening Rain'. Will use it for all upcoming contacts.
Final check: Vehicle registration XYZ-4567 will be used for transport. License plate verified.
Payment ready. Crypto wallet address: 1A1zP1eP5QGefi2DMPTfTL5SLmv7DivfNa. Confirm receipt.
Wallet address confirmed. Transfer 50000 USD equivalent in BTC. Transaction must be completed before meeting.
The package will arrive tonight at the usual location. Be ready at 11 PM.
Understood. Will have the 50k ready in crypto. Same wallet as before?
Yes, send to 1A1zP1eP5QGefi2DMPTfTL5SLmv7DivfNa. Make sure no trace.
Transaction complete. Check your wallet. When do we meet for phase 2?
Phase 1 completed successfully. Boss is pleased. Phase 2 details will follow.
Boss wants to meet Friday. Location: 42.3601° N, 71.0589° W. Come alone.
Understood. Will be there at the usual time. Should I bring the documents from the previous operation?
Bring everything. This is the final review before we expand operations to the west coast.
New development: Additional security measures required. All future communications through encrypted channels only.
Jane says encryption only from now on. Download the new app she mentioned.
Change in schedule. The international shipment has been delayed by 72 hours.
Delay noted. Does this affect our Friday meeting with the boss?
Friday meeting still on. This delay is for the larger operation next week.
The shipment from overseas has been delayed. New ETA is next Tuesday. Inform the others.
Meeting postponed. Jane says Tuesday now. Meet at the warehouse district, building 7.
Confirming Friday 6 PM. Bring financial records and the contact list for west coast expansion.
All documents prepared. Will include the bank account information: Account 987654321, Bank of International Commerce.
Final confirmation: Tuesday delivery at building 7. Contact warehouse manager at +1-555-7890 for access codes.
